package Assignment;

import java.util.TreeMap;
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Program32{
	public static void main(String[] args) {
		// TODO Auto-generated method stub

		TreeMap<Integer,String> tree=new TreeMap<Integer,String>();
		
		tree.put(1,"Tintu");
		tree.put(3,"Riya");
		tree.put(2,"Diya");
		tree.put(5,"Oviya");
		tree.put(4,"Lily");
		
		System.out.println("Original TreeMap is : "+tree);
		
		Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
		System.out.println("Enter The Starting Key : ");
		int x=sc.nextInt();
		System.out.println("Enter The Ending Key : ");
		int y=sc.nextInt();
		
		System.out.println("Sub Map Key-Values : "+tree.subMap(x,y));
		
		
	}

}
